TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, A.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP, (SUBSTR(A.STYLE_NUM,1,4)) AS STYLE_NUM, A.COLOR_CODE as COLOR_CODE, CASE WHEN TRIM(A.CUP_SIZE) IS NULL THEN '--' ELSE TRIM(A.CUP_SIZE) END as CUP_SIZE, TRIM(A.SIZE_NUM) as SIZE_NUM FROM SLBA_ITEM A where a.item_id in (select min(a.item_id) from slba_item a left join (select * from item where division_group = 'sli' and (substr(sku,15,2) = '00' or substr(sku,15,2) is null or substr(sku,1,2) = company_code or substr(sku,1,2) = 'XX')) b on a.item_id = b.item_id where a.division_group = 'sli' and b.item_id is null GROUP BY TRIM(A.DIVISION_GROUP),TRIM(A.COMPANY_CODE),TRIM(A.DIVISION_CODE),TRIM(A.STYLE_NUM),TRIM(A.COLOR_CODE),TRIM(A.SIZE_NUM),TRIM(A.CUP_SIZE) )

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE_NUM AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR_CODE AND CUP_SIZE = I_CUP_SIZE AND SIZE_NUM = I_SIZE_NUM AND DIVISION_GROUP = I_DIVISION_GROUP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY) as GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.BRAND_CODE),'1') as BRAND_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.COLOR_CODE),'1') as COLOR_CODE, TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_CODE) as DIVISION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SKU),'sls',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SKU),'sld',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SKU),'1') as SKU, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SIZE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SIZE_NUM),'slca',NVL(TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SIZE_NUM),1),'1') as SIZE_NUM, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',NVL(TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.CUP_SIZE),'1'),'1') as CUP_SIZE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM),'1') as STYLE_NUM, TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) <> 'sli' AND LOWER(TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP'))
